title: Facebook makes editorial decision to limit distribution of story claiming to show 'smoking gun' emails related to Biden and his son
text: Facebook made the decision to limit the distribution of a news article from the New York Post that claims to show 'smoking gun' emails related to Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden and his son.

title: Bill Gates on regulating Big Tech: 'We're in uncharted territory'
text: Microsoft founder Bill Gates joins CNBC's Becky Quick to discuss how more regulation could impact Big Tech companies as lawmakers scrutinize the biggest companies such as Google, Apple and Facebook.

title: Facebook to use artificial intelligence in bid to improve renewable energy storage
text: Facebook and Carnegie Mellon University have announced they are trying to use AI to find new "electrocatalysts" that can help to store electricity generated by renewables.

title: 4 Growth Stocks You Can Safely Hold Through 2030
text: These high-growth companies offer competitive advantages that'll favor buy-and-hold investors.
